37b52e5f624e441bbe6d8da42d4bd2?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0c37b52e5f624e441bbe6d8da42d4bd2?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1699192458, "last_modified": 1743751198}, "last_reply_by": "timeflies2020", "last_touched": 1743763634, "title": "问问各位大哥，你们会接受一个人自行到公司人事部来找工作么？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1123291", "created": 1743751870, "deleted": 0, "content": "最近一直找不到工作。\r\n所以我一个亲戚（非计算机领域）给我支了一招，让我直接去投简历的公司找他们人事直接问要不要人。然后看看能不能直接进行面试。\r\n他认为对于 HR 来说一个活生生的站在他面前的求职者比电子简历要好得多，所以建议我这么做。\r\n不知道各位大哥觉得这样做可以么？", "content_rendered": "最近一直找不到工作。<br />所以我一个亲戚（非计算机领域）给我支了一招，让我直接去投简历的公司找他们人事直接问要不要人。然后看看能不能直接进行面试。<br />他认为对于 HR 来说一个活生生的站在他面前的求职者比电子简历要好得多，所以建议我这么做。<br />不知道各位大哥觉得这样做可以么？", "last_modified": 1743751870, "replies": 39, "id": 1123291}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_large.png?m=1730363795", "name": "nas", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_normal.png?m=1730363795", "title": "NAS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/nas", "topics": 2662, "footer": "", "header": "关于网络存储设备的讨论", "title_alternative": "NAS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_mini.png?m=1730363795", "stars": 2733, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 949, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 193770, "username": "szsgz", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/szsgz", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c5b0/3cd6/193770_mini.png?m=1735801958", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c5b0/3cd6/193770_normal.png?m=1735801958", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c5b0/3cd6/193770_large.png?m=1735801958", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c5b0/3cd6/193770_xlarge.png?m=1735801958", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c5b0/3cd6/193770_xlarge.png?m=1735801958", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c5b0/3cd6/193770_xlarge.png?m=1735801958", "created": 1474990040, "last_modified": 1735801958}, "last_reply_by": "giganet", "last_touched": 1743760942, "title": "RAID0 停电，一个盘没了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1123252", "created": 1743730160, "deleted": 0, "content": "群晖 DS218+，两个 4T 硬盘组了 RAID0 ，前几天早上突然停电，油漆工在楼道里施工的时候不小心把我家碰跳闸了。\r\n\r\n再开机死活都起不来，最后拔掉一个反复尝试只装一个硬盘，冲刷系统等等。发现其中一个盘无论如何都无法写入。看起来正常，状态也是绿色，但是不管在群晖里还是在 windows 下都无法读写，显示什么 I/O 错误..\r\n\r\n现在我的群晖只剩一半的空间了。", "content_rendered": "群晖 DS218+，两个 4T 硬盘组了 RAID0 ，前几天早上突然停电，油漆工在楼道里施工的时候不小心把我家碰跳闸了。<br /><br />再开机死活都起不来，最后拔掉一个反复尝试只装一个硬盘，冲刷系统等等。发现其中一个盘无论如何都无法写入。看起来正常，状态也是绿色，但是不管在群晖里还是在 windows 下都无法读写，显示什么 I/O 错误..<br /><br />现在我的群晖只剩一半的空间了。", "last_modified": 1743730160, "replies": 31, "id": 1123252}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 28458, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3151, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 601590, "username": "sivanElliot", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/sivanElliot", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6595/bd64/601590_mini.png?m=1684926406", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6595/bd64/601590_normal.png?m=1684926406", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6595/bd64/601590_large.png?m=1684926406", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6595/bd64/601590_xlarge.png?m=1684926406", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6595/bd64/601590_xlarge.png?m=1684926406", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6595/bd64/601590_xlarge.png?m=1684926406", "created": 1668257089, "last_modified": 1684926406}, "last_reply_by": "echo314", "last_touched": 1743759073, "title": "国行 iPhone 17 系列接入 esim", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1123246", "created": 1743723486, "deleted": 0, "content": "估计国行 iPhone 大概率是 iPad 那个策略：<br>只能在境外添加非大陆运营商 esim ；<br>非国行在境内无法添加大陆 esim<br><br>那么港版 iPhone 等单实体卡的在大陆巨亏，双卡变单卡。", "content_rendered": "<p>估计国行 iPhone 大概率是 iPad 那个策略：<br/>只能在境外添加非大陆运营商 esim ；<br/>非国行在境内无法添加大陆 esim<br/><br/>那么港版 iPhone 等单实体卡的在大陆巨亏，双卡变单卡。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1743723486, "replies": 27, "id": 1123246}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "/static/img/node_default_large.png", "name": "computers", "avatar_normal": "/static/img/node_default_normal.png", "title": "计算机", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/computers", "topics": 484, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Computers", "avatar_mini": "/static/img/node_default_mini.png", "stars": 95, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 418, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 656196, "username": "sn0wdr1am", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/sn0wdr1am", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c6a7919632a1797e1f075dc31ffb0e87?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c6a7919632a1797e1f075dc31ffb0e87?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c6a7919632a1797e1f075dc31ffb0e87?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1698151564, "last_modified": 1739332865}, "last_reply_by": "f165af34d4830eeb", "last_touched": 1743764606, "title": "对于长时间高负载运行的任务，什么样的（小）主机适合？（比如编译 Android 源码）", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1123250", "created": 1743728068, "deleted": 0, "content": "对于长时间高负载运行的任务，什么样的（小）主机适合？（比如编译 Android 源码）\r\n\r\n不是那种低功耗，NAS 类型的。\r\n\r\n请各位巨佬推荐一下？\r\n\r\n自己在用的，计划配置的？\r\n\r\n主机或者小主机。\r\n\r\n自己组的，可以列下配置。\r\n\r\n谢谢大家。\r\n\r\nPS：在自己的 mbp 上跑编译+docker 打包，用了四五个小时。", "content_rendered": "<p>对于长时间高负载运行的任务，什么样的（小）主机适合？（比如编译 Android 源码）</p>\n<p>不是那种低功耗，NAS 类型的。</p>\n<p>请各位巨佬推荐一下？</p>\n<p>自己在用的，计划配置的？</p>\n<p>主机或者小主机。</p>\n<p>自己组的，可以列下配置。</p>\n<p>谢谢大家。</p>\n<p>PS：在自己的 mbp 上跑编译+docker 打包，用了四五个小时。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1743735258, "replies": 21, "id": 1123250}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_large.png?m=1650127623", "name": "shenzhen", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_normal.png?m=1650127623", "title": "深圳", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/shenzhen", "topics": 3293, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Shenzhen", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_mini.png?m=1650127623", "stars": 2042, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 21, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 671883, "username": "cust2008", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/cust2008", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2aa9e6879b1dceed0a09539b8a033cb5?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2aa9e6879b1dceed0a09539b8a033cb5?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2aa9e6879b1dceed0a09539b8a033cb5?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1705399623, "last_modified": 1705399623}, "last_reply_by": "ufs", "last_touched": 1743761078, "title": "深圳的电单车的横冲直撞，闯红灯，鸣笛，应该有政府负责还是找美团饿了么 顺丰，中通，圆通等平台负责，还市民一个安静的居住环境可以吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1123266", "created": 1743736524, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1743736524, "replies": 21, "id": 1123266}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1695370146", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1695370146", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 1987